$contents = array(
  array('id' => '1','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonetuesdayclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm" style="text-decoration: underline;">BritzoneTuesdayClass</span></span></a> Proudly Presents: <br/>&#34;<b>Paralinguistic</b>&#34; by Rocky Michael Tandi</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">Have you ever heard of Paralinguistic before?<br/>Is it some kind of an expression or words or is it how you make people understand what you say? Body language, gestures, facial expressions, tone and pitch are all examples of paralinguistic features.</p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>The research of Astrid Acosta (2014) shows that the paralinguistic features proved to be helpful and <br/>relevant to be considered when learning English. Paralinguistic features alert the listener as to how to interpret the message.</p><p>Now the question is how it affects your English learning? For those of you who already knew, do you want to share your thoughts about paralinguistic?</p><p>We, Tuesday’s class PIC would like to bring you a class activity that may improve your English Speaking skill conducted by Rocky Michael Tandi.</p><p>So please mark it in your calendar and save the date. Our Tuesday class will be held on November 29, 2016 and start at 18.30 until 20.00. Come join us at <a href="http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2FDetik.com%2F&amp;h=aAQER7_ZJAQFtUdPb9v1ffuAEt8Ukrg9P8lAQjQsVV0aFTw&amp;enc=AZOi9KavclrpNhQLaP4ngdRPAlFO0XVyuoMmnAxI63nMUBJuv32mJ7sfWcpNt0cElBlhToc3vM_cEIVJQjssmKQ7_MiT2VhxyOzdWSbMkadD7pBDsQgdAoVg2Tpndys6kz3iATbJsn4bh1Z_Penfi8RccfqPPHWr8xgVsiSRcfOulvByJ87q9AqTZPmCpKCEPK9RtLWD--FVcUwB89Sn4rLh&amp;s=1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">Detik.com</a> Redaction Office, on the 5th floor of Aldevco Building, Jl. Warung Buncit Raya No. 75 (Right in front of Buncit Indah Transjakarta\'s shelter), South Jakarta on.</p><p>Location link :</p><p><a href="http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en&amp;gl=gb" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en&amp;gl=gb</a></p><p>Note : Due to security reason, please bring along your ID card or a copy.</p><p>- Britzone is supported by <a href="http://detik.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">Detik.com</a> -<br/><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzoneid?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Britzoneid</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzone?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Britzone</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclub?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClub</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClass</span></span></a><br/>#<a href="http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2FDetik.com%2F&amp;h=oAQEWxh8cAQHFNAmdMqyDoG3126PScEv14YUXwsVIqLs50A&amp;enc=AZMDvQpPGyyBCzhAPQp_VlCBWOZo39Uh3Dk9X4jL_gXgLJFdn6s2LDcMs7JNN_Z3P09wX3UBcsiuDKayjUmo4NFUSY7ABHIw_z3GNtnjr2n1F9RmBKe9NnPp-9R4Fgaw2iFJAerNY0oJ1s7-y7xqfKBBZ0NNM2_p-ozHyhT8ENaK2wqIYdGUFeVWZY3kfBSVnqJBwfJgz_7c5iqFr04xXZDu&amp;s=1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">Detik.com</a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/p?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">p</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/bodylanguage?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">bodylanguage</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/gesture?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">gesture</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/paralinguistic?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1291001834275176" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">paralinguistic</span></span></a></p><p>See you there.</p></div><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','contentable_id' => '1','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-11-29 07:43:48','updated_at' => '2016-11-29 07:43:48','deleted_at' => NULL),
  array('id' => '2','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonespeakingacademy?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1292820597426633" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneSpeakingAcademy</span></span></a> proudly presents: Practice Giving Speech</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">A saying \'Practice Makes Perfect\' is used to convey that regular exercise of an activity or skill is the way to become proficient of it. It also can be used when encouraging someone to persist in something.</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">In presentation, practices or rehearsals are important to make our best performance. Practices provide opportunities to apply knowledge in different parts, see what works, and then put it regularly for a to<span class="text_exposed_show">tal presentation.</span></p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>Now, the thing is, are we going to do it in the class tonight? If you want to know more about it, then don\'t hesitate at all, just come and join us this Wednesday, on Nov 30, 2016. The class will be conducted by Bunga.</p><p>The class will be held at Warung Bang Diary, Jl. Anggrek Cakra No. 52, Kebon Jeruk, West Jakarta, from 18.30 to 20.00. Please stop at Kelapa Dua Sasak if you come by TransJakarta.</p><p>Here is the link location :<br/><a href="https://waze.to/lr/hqqgutweqq" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">Https://waze.to/lr/hqqgutweqq</a></p><p>See you all there. <br/><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzoneid?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1292820597426633" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">britzoneId</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzone?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1292820597426633" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Britzone</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/bsa?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1292820597426633" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BSA</span></span></a> <span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1292820597426633" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClass</span></a></span></p></div>','contentable_id' => '2','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-12-04 14:24:24','updated_at' => '2016-12-04 14:24:24','deleted_at' => NULL),
  array('id' => '3','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonefunday?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneFunDay</span></span></a> proudly presents:<br/>&#34;A Sneak Peek at Content Writing&#34; by Doni Sumitro</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">It will be held in Warung Bang Dairy, Jl. Anggrek Cakra No. 52, Kelap. Dua, Kebon Jeruk. Per usual, it will last from 11.00 to 13.00, so don\'t be late!</p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>Here\'s the link you can check out:<br/><a href="https://waze.to/lr/hqqgutweqq" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">https://waze.to/lr/hqqgutweqq</a></p><p>See you there!</p><p><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzoneid?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneID</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzone?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Britzone</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/bfd?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BFD</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclub?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClub</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClass</span></span></a><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/jakarta?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Jakarta</span></span></a> <span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/contentwriting?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1297033330338693" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">ContentWriting</span></a></span></p></div>','contentable_id' => '3','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-12-04 14:26:11','updated_at' => '2016-12-04 14:26:11','deleted_at' => NULL),
  array('id' => '4','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonetuesdayclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneTuesdayClass</span></span></a> Proudly Presents: How To Make a Good Impression in Communication</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">It takes just a quick glance, maybe three seconds, for someone to evaluate you when you meet for the first time. In this short time, the other person forms an opinion about you based on your appearance, your body language, your demeanor, your mannerisms, and how you are dressed.</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">With every new encounter, you are evaluated and yet another person\'s impression of you is formed when you communi<span class="text_exposed_show">cate with someone. These impressions can be nearly impossible to reverse or undo, making those encounters extremely important, for they set the tone for all the relationships that follows.</span></p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>So, whether they are in your career or social life, it\'s important to know how to create a good impression.</p><p>If you want to know more how to make good impression in communication, let’s clear your schedule because an Farhan Bestyardi will share his knowledge and experience.</p><p>Our Tuesday class will be held on December 6th, 2016, start at 18.30 until 20.00. It will be held at Warung Bang Diary,Jl. Anggrek Cakra No. 52, Kelapa Dua, Kebon Jeruk, West Jakarta.</p><p>Please click this link for location:<br/><a href="https://www.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwaze.to%2Flr%2Fhqqgutweqq&amp;h=-AQHn2ejDAQGhtAW4ASG2GzsdBTxvo90GZ2QTuQl0-wWcfw&amp;enc=AZO-KaH65jLIeAerQaeN3onZ0Lfo-IgQuKo7AeJVbExc4B_KODw-XgDZw2hkb4yXeU9iVL9DUiJdE3ogZNjf1eec-xrcZCxLHO1zbcI8rxXoqDWekomCjR8WEr6TtM1auno-iq_t1ZBeExIyRFsVMYyBzuKBdoBNj2nKWCUxgAc96Uz9XfnMH8SiUEG5lj98fhV16FZadwQaq8bLtcvej9Vr&amp;s=1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">https://waze.to/lr/hqqgutweqq</a><br/>See you there.<br/><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzoneid?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneID</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzone?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">britzone</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/jakarta?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">Jakarta</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclub?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClub</span></span></a> <a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/freeenglishclass?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1302243686484324" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">FreeEnglishClass</span></span></a></p></div><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','contentable_id' => '4','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-12-06 10:50:17','updated_at' => '2016-12-06 10:50:17','deleted_at' => NULL),
  array('id' => '5','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonespeakingacademy?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1303753133000046" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneSpeakingAcademy</span></span></a> proudly presents:</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">Public Speaking: &#34;Learning by Doing&#34; by Nitesh Gianchandhani</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">For the things we have to learn before we can do them, we learn by doing them.</p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>Aristotle</p><p>What do you think is the best way to learn something, is it by learning the theory first then practice it later? How about practice first and theory later, or even learning by doing? which one do you think is better?</p><p>Learning theory before practice is a method usually used by teachers to teach in the classroom. They do it because they think knowing the theory first will make the learning easier to grasp and the activity easier to do when they have to practice. But when it comes to public speaking, learning theory before practice may be impractical. Most teachers nowadays prefers to apply learning by doing in teaching. They find it more applicable for the students and less time consuming. How about you, do you find it better to learn public speaking by doing it?</p><p>If you want to find the answer to the question, then you\'d better save the date, clear your schedule and come join us in the last round of BSA public speaking class. We will learn how to do public speaking by doing it. The class will be conducted by Nitesh Gianchandhani, the public speaking expert, on Wednesday, Dec 7th, 2016 from 6.30 to 8 pm. It will be held in Detik\'s office, at Aldevco Octagon building, 5th floor, jl. Buncit Raya no 11, Pejaten, South Jakarta (right in front of Buncit Indah TransJakarta shelter).</p><p>Here is link address:<br/><a href="http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en%E2%89%B7%3Dgb" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);text-decoration: underline;">http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en≷=gb</a></p><p>Please don\'t forget to bring your ID card or a copy of it.<br/>See you all there!</p></div><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','contentable_id' => '5','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-12-07 07:06:30','updated_at' => '2016-12-07 07:07:08','deleted_at' => '2016-12-07 07:07:08'),
  array('id' => '6','content' => '<p style="font-size: 14px;"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/britzonespeakingacademy?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1303753133000046" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);"><span class="_5afx" style="direction: ltr;"><span class="_58cl _5afz">#</span><span class="_58cm">BritzoneSpeakingAcademy</span></span></a> proudly presents:</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">Public Speaking: &#34;Learning by Doing&#34; by Nitesh Gianchandhani</p><p style="font-size: 14px;">For the things we have to learn before we can do them, we learn by doing them.</p><div class="text_exposed_show" style="font-size: 14px;"><p>Aristotle</p><p>What do you think is the best way to learn something, is it by learning the theory first then practice it later? How about practice first and theory later, or even learning by doing? which one do you think is better?</p><p>Learning theory before practice is a method usually used by teachers to teach in the classroom. They do it because they think knowing the theory first will make the learning easier to grasp and the activity easier to do when they have to practice. But when it comes to public speaking, learning theory before practice may be impractical. Most teachers nowadays prefers to apply learning by doing in teaching. They find it more applicable for the students and less time consuming. How about you, do you find it better to learn public speaking by doing it?</p><p>If you want to find the answer to the question, then you\'d better save the date, clear your schedule and come join us in the last round of BSA public speaking class. We will learn how to do public speaking by doing it. The class will be conducted by Nitesh Gianchandhani, the public speaking expert, on Wednesday, Dec 7th, 2016 from 6.30 to 8 pm. It will be held in Detik\'s office, at Aldevco Octagon building, 5th floor, jl. Buncit Raya no 11, Pejaten, South Jakarta (right in front of Buncit Indah TransJakarta shelter).</p><p>Here is link address:<br/><a href="http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en%E2%89%B7%3Dgb" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 88, 153);">http://maps.google.com/?cid=16438735132135200288&amp;hl=en≷=gb</a></p><p>Please don\'t forget to bring your ID card or a copy of it.<br/>See you all there!</p></div><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','contentable_id' => '6','contentable_type' => 'App\\Post','created_at' => '2016-12-07 07:09:12','updated_at' => '2016-12-07 07:09:12','deleted_at' => NULL)
